ADDITIONAL NOTICE — NOT LEGAL ADVICE

VerdictAI is an educational and research tool. Its outputs — including answers,
citations, case analyses, simulated arguments, and simulated verdicts — are
generated by AI language models and may be incomplete, outdated, or incorrect.
They do NOT constitute legal advice, do NOT create a lawyer-client relationship,
and are NOT a prediction of any real court outcome. Always verify against the
primary legal texts and consult a qualified advocate for any real legal matter.

The legal texts (Acts) included in this repository under `data/pdf/` are public
documents of the Government of Nepal and remain subject to their own terms. The
MIT license above applies to the VerdictAI source code, not to those documents.
